ial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">先给放一张地图，以便了解各大酒店的地理方位。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" align="center" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><br></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">重庆两江酒店</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">两江酒店位于重庆秋糖的食品热点商圈</font>-红旗河沟的正中心，这里是重庆市双轨换乘中心，地理位置优越，交通十分便利。重庆市中心高端酒店群以两江酒店为龙头，北邻和府、渝通饭店，南有伊美、小天鹅、希尔顿酒店，商圈成熟。无论客商如何南来北往，两江酒店都是必经之处，是人气聚集的中心地带。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2014年秋季食品专区在两江酒店成功设展，两江酒店火爆的招商人气得到了很多企业的认可，因此，两江酒店也一举成为2014年重庆秋季糖酒会设展人气旺、效果好的酒店。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">轻轨路线</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">重庆市轻轨</font>3号线由北至南贯通全城，连接了重庆江北机场、重庆北站、红旗河沟、国际会展中心四大糖酒会交通热点。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-fami