<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">先给放一张地图，以便了解各大酒店的地理方位。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" align="center" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="http://pic.jiushang.cn/upload/web_app/11/2017/10/24/TkdfGX5BxQ.png" style="width: 100%;"><br></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">重庆两江酒店</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">两江酒店位于重庆秋糖的食品热点商圈</font>-红旗河沟的正中心，这里是重庆市双轨换乘中心，地理位置优越，交通十分便利。重庆市中心高端酒店群以两江酒店为龙头，北邻和府、渝通饭店，南有伊美、小天鹅、希尔顿酒店，商圈成熟。无论客商如何南来北往，两江酒店都是必经之处，是人气聚集的中心地带。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2014年秋季食品专区在两江酒店成功设展，两江酒店火爆的招商人气得到了很多企业的认可，因此，两江酒店也一举成为2014年重庆秋季糖酒会设展人气旺、效果好的酒店。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">轻轨路线</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">重庆市轻轨</font>3号线由北至南贯通全城，连接了重庆江北机场、重庆北站、红旗河沟、国际会展中心四大糖酒会交通热点。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">如果各位前来参展的企业和专业人士乘坐高铁或者飞机到达重庆，均可步行至就近的轻轨站点，乘坐轻轨</font>3号线，至红旗河沟站1口出站，即可到达两江酒店。而由会展中心至两江酒店也可步行至工贸站，乘坐轻轨3号线。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">公交路线</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">相关人士到达重庆北站后，公交</font>217、818、202、821路均可到达重庆两江酒店。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">机场方面，公交可乘坐</font>K001路，下车后步行800米即可到达重庆两江酒店</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 24.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">有去往会展中心的人士，从重庆两江酒店出发，可乘坐</font>872、115、319、145路公交至会展中心。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(69,69,69);font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-he